spec_data.Name: rubygem-sass
spec_data.Description:
Sass makes CSS fun again. Sass is an extension of CSS, adding
nested rules, variables, mixins, selector inheritance, and more.
It's translated to well-formatted, standard CSS using the
command line tool or a web-framework plugin.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 05:29:50 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A powerful but elegant CSS compiler that makes CSS fun again
